<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.293862>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Akodon polopi, new species (holotype MACN 23486): dorsal (upper left), ventral (upper right) and lateral (middle) views of skull and labial view (bottom) of mandible. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/293862/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.293863>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Akodon polopi, new species (holotype MACN 23486): live trapped specimen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/293863/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.293864>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Type locality and additional localities of Akodon polopi, new species (Province of Córdoba, Argentina)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/293864/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.293476>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. A. polopi, new species: Left upper (A) and left lower (B) molar rows in a young specimens (age class 2, CNP 1503). Scale = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/293476/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.293865>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Two different views, and habitat types, at the type locality of Akodon polopi, new species A) Steppe grasslands of Stipa sp. and Festuca hieronymii; B) Large stands of grasses of Paspalum quadrifarium and Poa stutckertii in rocky outcrops." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/293865/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

